column5: Are there any places to purchase diesel fuel on the bypass around Kenora, Highway 17A? Or would one have to go into Kenora? Bellbuoy
I think there is a Shell station on the East edge near intersection of 17 & 17A. Close to OPP. I'm just going by memory,,,,
You will have to go into town, The Shell station is right in town. I do not know of any stations on 17A. JJ
Redden's gas station on hwy 17 is just a couple of miles (km's) west of the eastern merge of 17 & 17A. Don't know if they have diesel though. You could call them and check: 807-548-4066
